articles.title: About this blog
articles.description: Time to particpate in the R community!
articles.contents: While I’ve been doing data analysis for decades, I’ve recently started using R (I previously used SAS) and I’ve appreciated seeing the articles written by members of the R community with different tips and techniques. This site is to share back and to collect my thoughts on the things I’m learning.
